Package: libghc-happstack-extra-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: ${haskell:Depends}
Description: Components built on top of Happstack+HSP
  A collection of components built on top of Happstack+HSP, including
  Google Analytics, a Calendar widget, and more.
  .
  Author: jeremy@n-heptane.com
  Upstream-Maintainer: jeremy@n-heptane.com
  .
  This package contains the normal library files.

